    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required gradation levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped as not-assessed consistent with MRL 2 requirements. Uncertainty quantification performed via Monte Carlo propagation over key inputs; output variance in relative hemolysis index is within acceptable bounds for the Class II device decision. The CFD model is deemed credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions under CPB use. RH < 1 criterion satisfied at all 5 evaluated operating points. Assessment team accepts the model for the stated COU.",
